CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 25, 1954, pg. 18 reads: "Grill Club Night Scores - With Joe Westray's crew on the scene at Crawford Grill Number Two every night...Some members of the Joe Westray band are (left to right) Westray, guitar and leader; Dolores Ware, vocalist, and Robin Webster, tenor sax...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Dolores Ware performing at microphone between Joe Westray on guitar, and Robin Webster on tenor saxophone, in Crawford Grill No. 2
